<h4>{t}CID{/t}</h4>
<p class="prInnerSmallTop">{t}A Card Security Code (CSC) or Card ID (CID) is a special security feature of your Visa, MasterCard, or American Express credit card.{/t}</p>
<p class="prInnerSmallTop">
{t}On your Visa or MasterCard it is a 3 digit number on the back of your card in the signature panel, following your 16-digit card number. {/t}</p>
<p class="prInnerSmallTop">
{t}On your American Express it is a 4 digit number on the front of your card above and to right of your card number.{/t} 
</p>		

